         Item Master (Catalog)
                │
                ▼
   Purchase Invoice / Purchase Receipt
                │
                ▼
   Item marked as "Is Fixed Asset?"
                │
                ▼
   Asset Creation (via Asset Category rules)
                │
                ▼
   Asset Document (Individual asset records)
                │
                ▼
   Asset Lifecycle Tracking
   (Capitalization → Depreciation → Transfer → Disposal)
